All Implemented Interfaces:
IDbDto, IObserver, ISubject, java.lang.Comparable<IDbDto>
public class SubSubClass
extends SubClass

A sub class of the sub class of the root class; provides a test object for testing operations on an inheritance hierarchy; the sub-sub class specializes the sub-class, which specializes the root class.

Author:
Bob Muller (muller@computer.org)
